v8:item.v8:content: Average earnings based on Social Insurance Fund data (EDI)
Insurance number of individual personal account
Earnings from all civil law contracts
Общая сумма заработка по всем страхователям ГПХ не превышающая предельной величиной базы страховых взносов. Учитываются только доходы включенные в базу страховых взносов.

Total amount of earnings of all civil law contract insurants that does not exceed the maximum amount of the insurance contribution base. Only income included in the insurance contribution base is considered.

Total amount of earnings of all insurants that does not exceed the maximum amount of the insurance contribution base. Only income included in the insurance contribution base is considered (since 2023 including civil law contracts).
Earnings from current civil law contract

Total amount of earnings of one (current) civil law contract insurant that does not exceed the maximum amount of the insurance contribution base. Only income included in the insurance contribution base is considered.
